    <item>
      <title>无人机飞行禁令扩展至纽约关键基础设施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/drone-flight-bans-extended-to-new-york-critical-infrastructure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国联邦航空管理局在宣布对新泽西州实施同样措施的第二天，就宣布了为期一个月的禁止无人机飞越纽约关键基础设施的禁令。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/drone-flight-bans-extended-to-new-york-critical-infrastructure</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 14:24:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克威胁关闭政府，众议院共和党领导人已准备好拨款计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/house-may-vote-on-temporary-fix-to-stop-shutdown-networks-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[众议院议长迈克·约翰逊周五上午与他的副手和民主党人制定了战略，如何在美国政府午夜关门期限之前迅速在众议院通过一项支出法案。此前，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普支持的一项法案于周四失败。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/house-may-vote-on-temporary-fix-to-stop-shutdown-networks-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 13:37:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将价值 40 亿美元的媒体公司股份转入儿子管理的信托基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/trump-moves-4-billion-trump-media-stake-into-trust-run-by-son</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普将其持有的媒体公司价值约 40 亿美元的股份转让给由其长子小唐纳德·特朗普控制的信托基金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/trump-moves-4-billion-trump-media-stake-into-trust-run-by-son</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 12:48:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾立法者冲突、法律变化考验总统赖昌星</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/taiwan-protests-lawmaker-clashes-show-test-to-lai-s-leadership</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾朝野政党之间掀起新一轮政治角力，引发街头抗议和议员争斗，这加剧了人们对赖清德总统是否有能力治理全球最危险的地缘政治热点地区之一的质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/taiwan-protests-lawmaker-clashes-show-test-to-lai-s-leadership</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 02:10:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
